          rule: "Regla de la potencia",
          explanation: `\u222B${v}^n d${v} = ${v}^{n+1}/(n+1), para n \u2260 \u22121.`,
          latex: `\\int ${v}^{${toTex(n)}}\\, d${v} = \\frac{${v}^{${toTex(n)}+1}}{${toTex(n)}+1}`
